title: The Alayah Drama, Plus: An Exclusive Clip
description:
Rachel and Becca weigh in on why last night’s episode was the beginning of the end for Alayah. Also, their take on how Peter is navigating the first three weeks of the season.  

Plus, an exclusive clip from next week’s episode of “The Bachelor.”

Don’t forget to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
